name: Anything and Everything Mix Ver 3
description:
The newest installation in my merge series! The model performs best with semi-realistic styles, edging a bit towards anime styles. Just as the other ones, this is a versatile model and has become my go-to for gens!

Compared to my previous merges, I this one has several improvements!

-More vivid colors

-Greater capability for details

-Greater ability to do hardcore imagery
